infra.name: te0803_4eg_2i
infra.description: Zynq UltraScale+ MPSoC TE0803-*-4GI21-A (4GB DDR) Board (form factor 5.2x7.6 cm) with 4x 1 GigaByte DDR4, speed grade -2 and industrial temperature range. *Supported PCB Revisions: REV03. Board Part is only with minimum PS-Setup. Use for own carrier or simple SDK debugging. User must configure B2B MIOs manually, depending on his carrier board connection. Without user PS configuration only JTAG and QSPI boot is possible with this board part file.
infra.author: trenz.biz
